      "body" : "I can restore the call to FormatMoney there and make utilmoneystr.o part of libconsensus only for one that reject reason line if that is preferred.\r\nIf you have another option in mind, please, say so.\r\n\r\nAlso, the python tests are failing because I have improved the information provided by the reject reason in https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/7287/files#diff-7ec3c68a81efff79b6ca22ac1f1eabbaR2989 At a first glance it doesn't seem trivial to adapt it to the new message, so the simplest option seems to be to just leave the same reject reason that we had (but then some information like the hash of the transaction will be lost in the error messages printed by the callers).",
